  <text x="250" y="300" fill="#d4d4d8" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif" text-anchor="middle">Nghiên cứu gốc 1985</text>
  <text x="250" y="318" fill="#d4d4d8" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif" text-anchor="middle">(Gilovich, Vallone, Tversky)</text>
